{"type": "article", "id": 8958, "title": "匡威 Slip-On", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-28T07:18:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135150j8pKGdUFzVy2N3Te.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t“Slip-On” 被叫做“一脚蹬”，这大概是这几年最火热的鞋子之一，翻译过来的这个词形象地表明了它便于穿脱，搭配方便地特点，一时成为了众多人的心头好。匡威最近对其旗下经典的 Jack Purcell 进行了一次升级，在原来的基础上加入了Nike Zoom Air 气垫技术，推出了更新版的“一脚蹬”，有蓝色，白色和黑色三种经典颜色可选。预计在本月内面市，喜欢匡威的大家可以保持关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351461kCDbGihsanBcVlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135147Ql6VstPRvJ0UuFcE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135147iYn9abHeKPL0DzFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135147fqgub2e7wIRs1lnz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135148fRD0gIPS4eFqWH3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135148HMWxdfy1hrvISZTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135149glS07GEm8tu4hM9C.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66575342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}